Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.23,0:00:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That's horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish you could've seen Hitoe\Ngetting all desperate and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:25.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, she was saying she was\Ngoing to protect Ru-ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Acting all cocky to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:28.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:32.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, once a nobody, always a nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:36.29,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to battle me\Nthat much, I'll battle you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:39.50,Main,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,She came!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not part of the fun, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:52.68,Main,,0,0,0,,\N--Lookie-lookie! Aki-lucky did
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:55.01,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ru...\N--exactly what you asked for, Urith!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:56.89,Main,,0,0,0,,--Tama's here.\N--It was a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:01:00.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko came here with her buddy-buddy Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:03.98,Main,,0,0,0,,So Aki-lovely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, um, um, so Urith,\Nwhat should I do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:08.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki-lu--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:19.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this the interesting show you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:24.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:25.71,Main,,0,0,0,,What a let down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:53.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taken and granted,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:57.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ideals are repetitious games that slip through{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:59.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My daily life is so shot with holes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I can barely stand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:04.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Empty theories without conclusions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dance steps along invisible rules{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final bell holding together{\i0}\N{\i1}the crumbling day rings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:17.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the scene I imagine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:20.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you're there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:23.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No forgiveness? No desires?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:32.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And still{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:36.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We cry "OPEN"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:41.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A future to get back and a world to destroy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:43.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wish to open. GOT IT?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now cross{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish you don't cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:55.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The future of light and dark,{\i0}\N{\i1}let's believe in the "future"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:03:01.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that they overlap to gain color again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.48,Main,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never seen that before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona is the Girl of Dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:22.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama is the Girl of Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:26.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not possible for dark to long for light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:31.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it because she went to the outside world?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Because she met Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.39,Main,,0,0,0,,...may make their stories...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:42.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,You brought them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What would you have done if someone saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:58.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith! I'm sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:03:59.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,\N--Whoops, Aki-lucky got scolded!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,--Shut up!\N--Whoops, Aki-lucky got scolded!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Aww... So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:12.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You know...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:16.38,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hitoe... It's all Hitoe's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:20.26,Main,,0,0,0,,That ugly four-eyed girl\Ndidn't have her LRIG card...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:23.01,Main,,0,0,0,,B-But, see? Ruko is here with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,How unpleasant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:25.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.94,Main,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:33.86,Main,,0,0,0,,To scar her in such a noticeable place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:35.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.32,Main,,0,0,0,,How unsightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Un...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:41.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Un... sight... ly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Unsightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:08.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Scars are best placed\Nwhere they can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:12.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Places like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:16.69,Main,,0,0,0,,...are softer, and easier to scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Get away from Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.16,Main,,0,0,0,,No need to be so afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:33.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,No... not in a frail girl like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:41.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Kominato Ruko and Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to battle you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:50.14,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I asked her to set a stage\Nthat you couldn't refuse, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:53.69,Main,,0,0,0,,--Unsightly...\N--...what tactless actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,--Unsightly... Scar...\N--Such a foolish girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:59.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You went through all this... But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,--Unsightly... Unsightly...\N--I want to break you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Break...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.78,Main,,0,0,0,,--Unsightly...\N--Things of beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:08.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Things of power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Things of splendor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Things of justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:16.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I love seeing them being broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:22.42,Main,,0,0,0,,All things are most brilliant\Nwhen they're being broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:31.52,Main,,0,0,0,,It started off small.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:37.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I kept breaking various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:43.11,Main,,0,0,0,,They went cold in my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:48.66,Main,,0,0,0,,When I was young, I was able to\Ndeceive the adults around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:51.12,Main,,0,0,0,,But that didn't last very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:01.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Then it struck me that it's fine\Nas long as no one finds out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:05.13,Main,,0,0,0,,All I need to do is leave a scar\Nwhere it can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:08.47,Main,,0,0,0,,That way, no one will say anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:13.10,Main,,0,0,0,,The softest place that can't\Nbe seen from the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,The heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:15.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Why you...! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not my taste to act crudely,\Ninflicting pain to someone directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I just lead people to hate themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,To hate their lives to the extent that\Nthey end their lives themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:42.34,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,A mistake led to discovery...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.76,Main,,0,0,0,,...and so I had to behave myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I acted like a good girl, and made friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:56.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I just had to break someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:08:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,The boredom was so great that\NI was the one who felt like dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:11.37,Main,,0,0,0,,...I met...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.83,Main,,0,0,0,,...an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Being a Selector is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry\Nabout others in the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:30.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You're free to hurt anyone\Nas much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:33.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Neither adults nor law have any relevance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I broke everyone to my heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:41.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Stepping on the wishes of others,\Nto make them lose hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,...and their spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:50.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:54.66,Main,,0,0,0,,...I can hear the girls' cries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:59.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Was that your wish...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:02.67,Main,,0,0,0,,To bring other people's lives to ruin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:07.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be within this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:12.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Within this vortex of sorrow, hate, and regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I wished to be an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:22.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? Can I really become an LRIG?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:28.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. A Selector deserving of you lies in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.82,Main,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,...that appearance of yours\Nis fitting beside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:46.96,Main,,0,0,0,,And so, you came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:54.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you were a bit too refined for my tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:10:00.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, has this ever crossed your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:03.69,Main,,0,0,0,,That the real world can just bite the dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.82,Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,...false images, deceit, and pretentious lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,But, the battlefield isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:18.66,Main,,0,0,0,,There is only truth there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Unsheathed battling for\None's desire, one's wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:29.00,Main,,0,0,0,,And... Splattered hearts lay in ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:34.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to watch forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.85,Main,,0,0,0,,...the despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:40.93,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll continue\Nto win my battles, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:43.85,Main,,0,0,0,,...repeat being an LRIG, forevermore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:51.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona, you want to do it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:54.95,Main,,0,0,0,,That is why you became Ru's LRIG after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Kominato Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:11:00.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the greatest Selector I have ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:05.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What sound will come\Nfrom shattering your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:08.67,Main,,0,0,0,,What kind of cries will you let out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:10.17,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:12.50,Main,,0,0,0,,No, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not my taste, but I\Ndidn't say I can't break you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:18.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do this, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:20.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:24.48,Main,,0,0,0,,She's serious. There's no telling\Nwhat she'll do if you refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:25.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to save Hitoe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko, don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:33.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:46.12,Main,,0,0,0,,If I win, let Hitoe go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:48.46,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:51.04,Main,,0,0,0,,That's "if" you win...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:12:00.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru... Such straightforward and beautiful eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:04.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll carve despair into those eyes of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:06.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:36.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:40.55,Main,,0,0,0,,...Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, Kominato speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, Uemura-{\i1}san{\i0}. I appreciate\Nyou for having Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:05.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Hitoe-{\i1}chan {\i0}hasn't returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.29,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not answering your calls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama... Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Unsightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Urie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:35.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow! Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Here I go, Tama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:43.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}! Death Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:53.42,Main,,0,0,0,,As expected, Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:57.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Breaking you is going to be well worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:59.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Skyju, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:01.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Burst! No Gain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.93,Main,,0,0,0,,They're both battling seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:13.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like Urith's having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Aki-lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:16.56,Main,,0,0,0,,--No...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,My Urith...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:23.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru is entering my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.57,Main,,0,0,0,,"Black Crisis"\NRu is entering my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:29.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Light... is spreading within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,So you are serious, Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You're seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru... Tama knows, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:41.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama has the same feelings as Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop, Tama-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to save Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,To do that, I have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:52.43,Main,,0,0,0,,"Servant One"\NRuko... For that, you'll even sacrifice Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:54.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:58.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama understands...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:04.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:10.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see Ruko and\NTama-{\i1}chan {\i0}hurting each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama likes Hitoe a lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.08,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:22.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll battle... serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:26.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Vimana, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:40.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:41.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all because I was caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:48.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm the reason why Ruko and Tama-{\i1}chan {\i0}are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't look away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:01.42,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:08.26,Main,,0,0,0,,All we can do is watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.68,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:15.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:18.64,Main,,0,0,0,,...we shouldn't look away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:27.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Such a beautiful style of battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,She really is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:35.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I can see why you laid eyes on her, Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let you savor something\Nthis amazing yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You and me--No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:47.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's savor this in full, along with Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:53.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll love you with pain until\Nyou raise a sweet shriek, Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:01.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:05.07,Main,,0,0,0,,...Urith so happy before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:08.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I've... never seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:10.99,Main,,0,0,0,,How unsightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Un... Un... sightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Unsightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Things of beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:30.72,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:34.68,Main,,0,0,0,,...loves me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:37.81,Main,,0,0,0,,She... loves me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira is Urith's Aki-lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki-lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:44.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki-lovely... Aki-lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama! Arc Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.71,Main,,0,0,0,,The battle isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Ener Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:08.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru! Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:12.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:15.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry and beat Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:18.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:20.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:29.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:32.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:34.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:41.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything is shining in white...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:50.84,Main,,0,0,0,,That strange thing is happening again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:54.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Dark crossing with light...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:57.35,Main,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:19:00.14,Main,,0,0,0,,...Ru is making things interesting after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Level 5?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:19.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Color Milulun surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.49,Main,,0,0,0,,...lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:21.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki-lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:23.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki... lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Dark Matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:49.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Baroque Defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:51.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Milulun knows that-lun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:54.94,Main,,0,0,0,,It can negate any attack, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:02.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:05.41,Main,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,So... strong. Ru... Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:16.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama... might lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:17.93,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe's... going to be saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:27.81,Main,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:30.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama... is light...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:36.19,Main,,0,0,0,,There once was a certain girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:43.79,Main,,0,0,0,,She was in solitude from the moment\Nshe was born into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:49.54,Main,,0,0,0,,She didn't know the world outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,...and was neither loved\Nnor touched by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:21:00.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ever and ever, she lived a life in\Nsolitude that felt like an eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:10.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember Futase Fumio's story?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:16.65,Main,,0,0,0,,The girls of dark and light\Nwere originally from one girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.53,Main,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:21.45,Main,,0,0,0,,...the original girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:24.45,Main,,0,0,0,,And... She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:26.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:28.87,Main,,0,0,0,,...our mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.04,Main,,0,0,0,,So bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:39.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:48.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Just when everyone was having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:54.40,Main,,0,0,0,,...you had to make everyone feel terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:56.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona is a bad girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:59.07,Main,,0,0,0,,She brings misery...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,"That Lie a Scar"\N...as the Girl of Dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:09.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A city of mazes with no exit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:19.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the sound of bells ringing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:27.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave the "now" handed to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:31.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as I begin to walk in the morning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a world where light and dark intersect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:43.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}catharsis begins to awake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:48.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swore in my shaking heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:58.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I won't lose anyone anymore...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.26,0:23:05.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if my tears flow tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:12.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll run through the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.06,0:23:17.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Release myself towards the future I selected{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.06,0:23:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to regain it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:26.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't give up on my wish{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:34.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru entered me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:37.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It felt nice and warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:39.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Frie... nd...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.34,0:23:42.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Something is... entering Tama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:44.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess everyone was just being played with...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:47.05,Main,,0,0,0,,"This World is My Property"\NThis World is My Property.
